---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">How to Spot and Remove Tech Support Scams in 2026</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>Tech support scams remain one of the most common threats to everyday computer users. Here's how to recognize them and what to do if you've been targeted.</p>

            <h2>Common Signs of a Tech Support Scam</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Unsolicited pop-up warnings claiming your computer is infected</li>
                <li>Calls from “Microsoft” or “Windows Support”</li>
                <li>Pressure to act immediately or your computer will be locked</li>
                <li>Requests for remote access to your PC</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>What to Do If You See a Scam</h2>
            <p>Do not call the number on the screen. Close the window or restart your computer. Then contact a trusted technician like RigRescue for a proper diagnostic.</p>
            <p><strong>Important:</strong> If you didn’t call the number, you’re very likely safe. If you did allow remote access, we can help! Most scam infections are easy to clean up — usually no more than the cost of our diagnostic.</p>

            <h2>How RigRescue Can Help</h2>
            <p>We specialize in remote virus/malware removal and scam cleanup. Our $50 diagnostic is always credited toward the full repair, and we never start work without your approval.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact"
                   class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Scam Cleanup Help Today
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
